<div id="pf4" class="pf w0 h6" data-page-no="4"><div class="pc pc4 w0 h6"><div class="t m97 x10 h14 y7a ff1 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Meet the </div><div class="t m98 x33 h14 y7b ff1 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Author of </div><div class="t m7c x33 h14 y7c ff1 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">This </div><div class="t m99 x33 h14 y7d ff1 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Quarter&apos;s </div><div class="t m9a x10 h14 y7e ff1 fsd fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Lessons </div><div class="t m9b x34 h15 y7f ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Russell Holt is associate editor of </div><div class="t m9c x35 h15 y7f ff5 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Signs of the Times. </div><div class="t m9d x14 h15 y7f ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">He has served </div><div class="t m9e x33 h15 y80 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">as executive editor of </div><div class="t m9f x12 h15 y80 ff5 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Ministry </div><div class="t ma0 x36 h15 y80 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and on the editorial staff of </div><div class="t ma1 x37 h15 y80 ff5 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">These </div><div class="t ma2 x33 h15 y81 ff5 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Times. </div><div class="t ma3 x1a h15 y81 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">He began his denominational career as a pastor in Indiana and </div><div class="t ma4 x33 h15 y82 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Arizona. </div><div class="t ma5 x34 h15 y83 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Elder Holt enjoys getting involved in do-it-yourself projects, read-</div><div class="t ma6 x33 h15 y84 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ing, and studying the American Civil War era. He has written numer-</div><div class="t ma7 x33 h15 y85 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ous&apos; articles for religious and secular periodicals. He and his wife, </div><div class="t ma8 x33 h15 y86 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Judy, have a son and a daughter. </div><div class="t ma9 x33 h9 y87 ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Blessing of Daily Study </div><div class="t maa x38 h15 y88 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Every day some portion of time should be appropriated to the </div><div class="t mab x39 h15 y89 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">study of the lessons, not merely in learning to mechanically repeat the </div><div class="t mac x39 h15 y8a ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">words, while the mind does not comprehend the meaning; but to go to </div><div class="t mad x39 h15 y8b ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the very foundation, and become familiar with what is brought out in </div><div class="t mae x39 h15 y8c ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the lesson. </div><div class="t maf x3a h15 y8d ff5 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;—Counsels on Sabbath School Work, </div><div class="t mb0 x3b h15 y8e ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">p. 53. </div><div class="t mb1 x39 h9 y8f ff1 fs4 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Daily Lesson Study Pledge </div><div class="t mb2 xf h16 y90 ff6 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">❑ </div><div class="t mb3 x38 h15 y91 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">As one greatly desirous of improving my knowledge of the Scrip-</div><div class="t mb4 xf h15 y92 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tures and of the Lord to whom they point, I pledge to carefully and </div><div class="t mb5 xf h15 y93 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">prayerfully study some portion of the Sabbath School lesson each day </div><div class="t mb6 xf h15 y94 ff2 fse fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the week. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
